Package: littag
Title: Lit-tag: an app for custom annotation of a citation database
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul", "McElhany", , "paul.mcelhany@noaa.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Starting with a citation library exported from Zotero, the
    lit-tag builder interface allows the creation custom annotation tags
    and notes. The lit-tag view module provides options to search the
    annotated database, generate custom reports, create summary graphics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/pmcelhany/lit-tag
